   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <note class="- topic/note ">An example system is used to illustrate the operating modes.
The function of the operating mode is similar in all applicable configurations,
but the energized path will depend on the configuration.</note>
         <p platform="PxW" class="- topic/p ">The operating mode depends on the status of the system,
the rectifier mains, the battery and the bypass mains.</p>
         <p platform="WxW" class="- topic/p ">The operating mode depends on the status of the system,
the DC input power and the bypass mains.</p>
         <p platform="PxW WxW" class="- topic/p ">The operating priority is:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
               <li platform="PxW WxW" class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">
                     <xref href="Normal_Operation_CPT_0000319413.dita"
                           scope="local"
                           type="concept"
                           class="- topic/xref "/>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li platform="PxW" class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">
                     <xref href="Battery_Operation_CPT_0000319411.dita"
                           scope="local"
                           type="concept"
                           class="- topic/xref "/>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li otherprops="generalM 2pMBS 3pMBS noMBS"
                   platform="PxW WxW"
                   class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">
                     <b otherprops="generalM" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">For systems with bypass: </b>
                     <xref href="Bypass_Operation_System_Operation_CPT_0000319410.dita"
                           scope="local"
                           type="concept"
                           class="- topic/xref "/>
                  </p>
               </li>
            </ol>
         </p>
         <p platform="SDC" class="- topic/p ">The operating mode of the system depends
on the status of the rectifier mains and the charge mode of the system.
The operation modes are:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">
                     <xref href="SDC_Float_Charge_CPT_0000536863.dita"
                           scope="local"
                           type="concept"
                           class="- topic/xref "/>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">
                     <xref href="SDC_Boost_Charge_CPT_0000531631.dita"
                           scope="local"
