                           class="- topic/xref "/>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">
                     <xref href="Battery_Operation_CPT_0000319411.dita"
                           scope="local"
                           type="concept"
                           class="- topic/xref "/>
                  </p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Other modes that the system can be in during startup,
charging, maintenance, troubleshooting and shutdown are:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li otherprops="generalM 2pMBS 3pMBS"
                   platform="PxW WxW"
                   class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">
                     <b otherprops="generalM" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">For systems with manual bypass switch(es): </b>
